# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# AI agent local config
.gemini/
/.claude/
.codex/
.codex-remote-attachments/
# 项目级 AI 指引：本地保留供 Claude Code 加载，不公开到开源仓库
/CLAUDE.md

# dependencies
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
/coverage

# next.js
/.next/
/out/

# production
# 注意：/build 同时是 electron-builder 的 buildResources 目录（图标、安装脚本等构建源资产）。
# 这些源文件必须入库——否则 CI 干净 checkout 拿不到，桌面端图标会回退成默认 Electron 图标。
/build
!/build/
/build/*
!/build/icon.ico
!/build/installer.nsh

# misc
.DS_Store
*.key
*.pem
.idea/

# debug
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*
!.env.example

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# electron
/dist
/dist-*
/local-clients-v*/
/data
/_standalone

# release/build scratch — installers, update metadata, patches (publish via GitHub Releases, never commit)
.tmp/

# sensitive config
mcp_config.json

# internal docs, plans, drafts (any language/naming)
/docs/
/AI每日深度简报_*.md
方案*/
计划*/
*草稿*/
*draft*/

# mobile apps (private repos — NEVER commit)
/mobile
/mobile_ios
*.dart

# closed-source product workspaces (private repos — NEVER commit here)
/author-pro
/reader
/reader-mobile
/reader-cloud

# mobile UI mockups & design artifacts (private)
home_screen.html
stitch*

# firebase local cache
.firebase/

